snippet.description:

Hi! 

This is No Title. It's my favorite song by Reol. This is, far and away, the hardest swing arrangement I had to do, so I'm definitely thankful that I had ThatTromboneGuy help me out with the mastering. 

Also, rip REOL (the group.) Y'all produced some amazing songs. :c


Composition/Vocals: Will Stetson
Mixing/Mastering: ThatTromboneGuy
